    "1": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "**GenericUtility Platform** — Polyglot microservices (20 services, 10 languages) running on AKS.\n\n**Apps:** Customer Billing (.NET 6) · Outage Analytics (Node.js, Java, Python, Go, Ruby, PHP, Elixir, Kotlin, Rust, .NET)\n\n**Namespaces:** `utility-customer-billing` · `utility-outage-analytics`"
    },
